US BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, AS TRUSTEE FOR CREDIT SUISSE FIRST BOSTON 2005-9, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Suzanne D. MACDOWELL, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Mr. MacDowell, Husband of Suzanne D. MacDowell, and Mortgage Electronic Registration Systems, Inc., as Nominee for Credit Suisse First Boston Financial Corporation, Defendants. C-583 September Term 2018
081543 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005056-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
